To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, this license grants rights similar in spirit to permissive open-source licenses, while preserving truthful representation requirements for the STOCRS-R name and reference implementation.

If any provision is found unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.

---

## Nature of Release

This is a minimal, self-contained reference implementation.

It is intended to demonstrate a structural application resolution model — not to represent a full production programming framework, runtime environment, or operating system.

Behavioral guarantees apply only within the scope of the reference model and its defined structural assumptions.

